General.Name: Social Media Venture
General.Description: Social Media Ventures, Inc., an online media venture company, creates and acquires social networking Websites. The company also operates two social networking sites petsplaces.com and rocktag.us, as well as provides local Internet services. In addition, it purchases, builds, operates, and sells Websites. The company was formerly known as NetSky Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Social Media Ventures, Inc. in May 2008. Social Media Ventures, Inc. was founded in 1998 and is based in Jericho, New York.
